"{\"uid\": \"glasgowtimes.co.uk-news-scottish-news-24100985.taekwondo-champ-picked-team-gb-mascot-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"South LanarkshireEntertainmentEventsLeisureSportEast KilbrideScotland  A nine-year-old taekwondo champ is 'buzzing' after being selected as a Team GB mini mascot for the 2024 Paris Olympic Games this summer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999259957831, \"rank\": 5.1420008730266037e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh Davidson, from East Kilbride, was one of six youngsters (and the only Scottish kid) picked for the role, having beaten more than\\u00a020,000 five to 11-year-olds across the UK who applied.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 209, \"end\": 213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_College\", \"score\": 0.9999957817506422, \"rank\": 4.218072069318352e-06, \"text\": \"Davidson\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_College\"}, {\"begin\": 229, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Kilbride\", \"score\": 0.9999969785922246, \"rank\": 3.021416830573249e-06, \"text\": \"East Kilbride\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Kilbride\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Kilbride\"}, {\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999826461549347, \"rank\": 1.7354039522997668e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh, and his other mini mascots, will support Team GB athletes as they prepare to compete in\\u00a0Paris, from kitting out - where athletes collect their kit In Birmingham - to local team announcements and participating in fan zones to watch the action.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999022074965, \"rank\": 9.779260247181988e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 555, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"score\": 0.9999812937197708, \"rank\": 1.8692848072067796e-05, \"text\": \"Birmingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very excited as only six people will get to be a mini mascot for the Paris Olympics,\\\" Josh said.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"It feels even more special because I am the only mascot fromScotland.\\\"\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh's dad, Mark Davidson, added: \\\"He's buzzing, and he actually found out a couple of months ago, so he has done really well not mentioning it.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Davidson\", \"score\": 0.9999611591314445, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mark Davidson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Davidson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Davidson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so chuffed for him.\\\"\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The six youngsters - who each represent the nations which make up Team GB - first met one another last year as they participated in a photo shoot and meet-and-greet with Olympic silver medallist, Mallory Franklin.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1212, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mallory_Franklin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mallory Franklin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mallory_Franklin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mallory_Franklin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, how did this South Lanarkshire superstar\\u00a0get picked for such a cool role?\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lanarkshire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6920889116150732e-15, \"text\": \"Lanarkshire\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lanarkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lanarkshire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, it all began with a ballot and a random selection process.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark explained: \\\"Angela (Josh's mum and Mark's wife) applied to a ballot around Autumn last year, which was open to all kids in the UK aged between like five and 11 or 12.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999826461549347, \"rank\": 1.7354039522997668e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From that, 40 kids were selected at random - one of which was Josh.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We then had to submit a video on why he should be picked as a mini mascot and his\\u00a0reasons for wanting to be involved in the process as well as hishistorywith sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Josh's history with sport is certainly an incredible one.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having started\\u00a0Taekwondo classes at the\\u00a0age of three, the youngster\\u00a0quickly grew into somewhat of a superstar in the popular martial art form.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With his blue belt now in the bag, the school pupil has travelled all over theworldwinning trophies and medals as well as making a name for himself.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark said: \\\"We are really proud of what he has achieved at such a young age.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He trains three to four times a week\\u00a0and competes nationally between four and six times a year and internationally once a year.\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He just performed at the Dutch Open in Holland and won a silver medal in the under-12s category.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9930590505371862, \"rank\": 0.005297046183640896, \"text\": \"Holland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has such an incredible passion for the sport, and he wants to be the best in the country.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so proud to support him.\\\"\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh added: \\\"I love competing and meeting new people and keeping fit.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2587, \"end\": 2591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9892087824480801, \"rank\": 0.01072357214038749, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I also enjoy learning new skills when I am training.\\\"\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympic Summer Games\\u00a0will take place between July 26 and August 11.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, clickHERE  This website and associated newspapers adhere to the Independent Press Standards Organisation's     Editors' Code of Practice.\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have a complaint about the editorial content which relates to     inaccuracy or intrusion, then pleasecontact the editor here.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are dissatisfied with the response provided you cancontact IPSO here  \\u00a9 2001-2025.\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Glasgow Timesis owned and operated by Newsquest Media Group Ltd, an audited local newspaper network.\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3188, \"end\": 3195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999983979251, \"rank\": 1.164885563782656e-09, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}, {\"begin\": 3226, \"end\": 3251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Newsquest Media Group L